	<title>Post Editor: Tapping the back button do dismiss the keyboard changes text fields.</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">Nexus One, 2.3.6
Go to the post editor.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.2">Tap in the content field to invoke the keyboard.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.3">Tap the back button to dismiss the keyboard.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.4">The cursor is now in the title field.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.5">Try this with the title and tags fields.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.6">Notice the cursor remains in the correct text field after dismissing the keyboard.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
